
* Type 'set vt100' if you wish to have ANSI features.

* Type 'chinese' if your terminal accepts Big-5 code and you wish to see
  Chinese.

* If you wish join building the world, Email to mud@cisppc2.cis.nctu.edu.tw

* FTP daemon now works! ftp to 140.113.23.241 port 8008. You can login with
  your name and password as in mud. Anonymous ftp is also available. For
  more information, see 'help ftp'.

* TYPE "help policy" TO SEE THE POLICY, IMPORTANT FOR WIZZES.

* TYPE "help rules" TO SEE THE RULES.

* Now ES is fixing something, you can play, BUT your character will
  be deleted when ES reopen.
